item.title: Help me please
item.dc:creator: @purez4life purez4life
item.description:
@purez4life wrote:

You have to have a server to play on.

  1. download a server source from the downloads section
  2. (scan it just incase of trojans) lol
  3. unzip it where you want it to be
  4. compile (to make any changes the last owner didn’t compile)
  5. double click “run” or “runserver”
    Hope this helped lol
